author: Xbox
description:
Experience an anomaly-hunting horror game inspired by liminal spaces and psychological horror walking simulators.

The Cabin Factory is out on Xbox now!
https://www.xbox.com/games/store/the-cabin-factory/9NL6BB89092T

Your job at the Cabin Factory is simple - inspect the cabins and decide whether they’re haunted or not. And if you find any anomalies, get out… immediately. 

FEATURES:
- An atmospheric horror experience - explore haunted cabins alone and try not to lose your sanity, 
- A compact story - experience the entire game in a single evening,
- Available in 13 languages - choose your preferred one and fully immerse yourself in the game.

description:
Inside ROG Xbox Ally is an educational video series designed to highlight platform-centric benefits—like Xbox Play Anywhere—so players can unlock the full potential of their ROG Xbox Ally.

Xbox Play Anywhere:
When you own a game that is Xbox Play Anywhere, it’s yours to play across the Xbox ecosystem on PC and Xbox console at no additional cost. Just log in with your Xbox account on your ROG Xbox Ally X or ROG Xbox Ally and download the game. It’s that easy. Pick up where you left off on console or PC – bringing all your saves, game add-ons, and achievements with you.*
Learn more: https://www.xbox.com/handhelds/rog-xbox-ally

*Requires internet connection. PC hardware requirements may vary for games on Windows 10/11.
